ugh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EInvesting%20is%20best%20for%20long-term%20financial%20goals%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESalinas%20points%20out%20that%20from%20a%20planning%20perspective%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20your%20short-term%20goals%20align%20with%20your%20longer-term%20goals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20shouldn't%20think%20of%20them%20as%20separate%2C%20individually%2C%20mutually%20exclusive%20items.%20They're%20all%20working%20in%20unison%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Salinas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvesting%20your%20money%20can%20be%20worthwhile%20for%20long-term%20goals%20of%20five%20years%20or%20more%2C%20like%20reaching%20retirement.%20You%C2%A0can%20get%20higher%20returns%20in%20the%20long%20run%20if%20you%20invest%20instead%20of%20saving%20it%20in%20a%20bank%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20holistic%20approach%20to%20your%20financial%20strategy%20can%20help%20you%20make%20the%20most%20out%20of%20money%20for%20both%20now%20and%20in%20the%20future.%20It%20can%20also%20provide%20clarity%20on%20how%20to%20navigate%20shifting%20economic%20conditions%20in%20a%20way%20that%20benefits%20all%20your%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsaving-money-smarter-than-investing-even-as-stock-market-soars-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730545202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67196d849b3250dbbce9a6a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsaving-money-smarter-than-investing-even-as-stock-market-soars-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20the%20stock%20market%20performing%20well%20after%20the%20Fed%20cut%20rates%2C%20saving%20money%20may%20still%20be%20smarter%20than%20investing%20it%20if%20you%20need%20to%20access%20it%20soon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sacevedo%40businessinsider.com%20(Sophia%20Acevedo)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsaving-money-smarter-than-investing-even-as-stock-market-soars-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Canadian%20Diplomat%20Summoned%20After%20Allegations%20Against%20Amit%20Shah%20By%20Minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERubbishing%20a%20Canadian%20minister's%20claims%20that%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20had%20ordered%20the%20targeting%20of%20Khalistani%20extremists%20in%20the%20country%2C%20India%20has%20termed%20them%20%26quot%3Babsurd%20and%20baseless%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20a%20Canadian%20diplomat%20had%20been%20summoned.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanada's%20Deputy%20Foreign%20Affairs%20Minister%20David%20Morrison%20had%20made%20the%20allegations%20while%20addressing%20members%20of%20the%20country's%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Public%20Safety%20and%20National%20Security%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReplying%20to%20a%20question%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20Spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20said%20a%20representative%20of%20the%20Canadian%20High%20Commission%20had%20been%20summoned%20on%20Friday%20and%20a%20diplomatic%20note%20was%20handed%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20conveyed%20in%20the%20note%20that%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20protests%20in%20the%20strongest%20terms%20to%20the%20absurd%20and%20baseless%20references%20made%20to%20the%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20of%20India%20before%20the%20committee%20by%20Deputy%20Minister%20David%20Morrison%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaiswal%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Morrison%20had%20said%20that%20he%20had%20confirmed%20Mr%20Shah's%20name%20to%20The%20Washington%20Post%2C%20which%20had%20first%20reported%20the%20allegations%2C%20and%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20said%20this%20proves%20that%20high-ranking%20Canadian%20officials%20deliberately%20leak%20unfounded%20claims%20to%20the%20media.%20Mr%20Jaiswal%20warned%20that%20such%20actions%20will%20have%20%26quot%3Bserious%20consequences%26quot%3B%20for%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20Canada.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20the%20revelation%20that%20high%20Canadian%20officials%20deliberately%20leak%20unfounded%20insinuations%20to%20the%20international%20media%20as%20part%20of%20a%20conscious%20strategy%20to%20discredit%20India%20and%20influence%20other%20nations%20only%20confirms%20the%20view%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20long%20held%20about%20the%20current%20Canadian%20government's%20political%20agenda%20and%20behavioural%20pattern.%20Such%20irresponsible%20actions%20will%20have%20serious%20consequences%20for%20bilateral%20ties%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECategorisation%2C%20Surveillance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20reports%20that%20Canada%20has%20named%20India%20an%20%26quot%3Badversary%26quot%3B%20alongside%20China%2C%20North%20Korea%20Russia%20and%20Iran%20in%20its%20National%20Cyber%20Threat%20Assessment%2C%20Mr%20Jaiswal%20said%20this%20was%20another%20example%20of%20imputations%20being%20made%20without%20evidence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20appears%20to%20be%20another%20example%20of%20a%20Canadian%20strategy%20to%20attack%20India.%20As%20I%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20their%20senior%20officials%20have%20openly%20confessed%20that%20they%20are%20seeking%20to%20manipulate%20global%20opinion%20against%20India.%20As%20on%20other%20occasions%2C%20imputations%20are%20made%20without%20any%20evidence%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20spokesperson%20also%20said%20some%20of%20India's%20consular%20officials%20were%20informed%20by%20the%20Canadian%20government%20that%20they%20have%20been%20under%20surveillance%20and%20said%20this%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bflagrant%20violation%26quot%3Bof%20diplomatic%20conventions.%20He%20also%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20New%20Delhi%20sees%20the%20action%20as%20a%20form%20of%20harassment%20and%20intimidation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20our%20consular%20officials%20were%20recently%20informed%20by%20the%20Canadian%20government%20that%20they%20have%20been%20and%20continue%20to%20be%20under%20audio%20and%20video%20surveillance.%20Their%20communications%20have%20also%20been%20intercepted.%20We%20have%20formally%20protested%20to%20the%20Canadian%20government%20as%20we%20deem%20these%20actions%20to%20be%20a%20flagrant%20violation%20of%20relevant%20diplomatic%20and%20consular%20conventions%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaiswal%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20citing%20technicalities%2C%20the%20Canadian%20Government%20cannot%20justify%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20is%20indulging%20in%20harassment%20and%20intimidation.%20Our%20diplomatic%20and%20consular%20personnel%20are%20already%20functioning%20in%20an%20environment%20of%20extremism%20and%20violence.%20This%20action%20of%20the%20Canadian%20Government%20aggravates%20the%20situation%20and%20is%20incompatible%20with%20established%20diplomatic%20norms%20and%20practices%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDiwali%20Celebrations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20Canada's%20opposition%20leader%20Pierre%20Poilievre%20cancelling%20Diwali%20celebrations%20that%20were%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20at%20Parliament%20Hill%20in%20Ottawa%2C%20sparking%20a%20backlash%20from%20the%20Indian%20community%2C%20Mr%20Jaiswal%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20some%20reports%20in%20this%20regard.%20It%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20the%20prevailing%20atmosphere%20in%20Canada%20has%20reached%20high%20levels%20of%20intolerance%20and%20extremism.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20reduction%20in%20the%20number%20of%20visas%20by%20the%20Canadian%20government%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20ministry%20is%20monitoring%20the%20well-being%20of%20students%20and%20temporary%20workers%20from%20India%20who%20are%20currently%20in%20Canada%20and%