f2d247ce3009a0fac8da88%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETravelers%20enter%20Jackson%20Hole%20Airport.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJAC%20is%20one%20of%20the%20smallest%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-20-best-airports-in-world-according-to-passengers-list-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emost%20luxurious%20airports%20in%20the%20country%3C%2Fa%3E.%20After%20deplaning%2C%20I%20stepped%20into%20a%20sparkling%20clean%20terminal%20that%20looked%20more%20like%20an%20upscale%20ski%20lodge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDesigned%20to%20feel%20like%20a%20living%20room%2C%20the%20space%20had%20wooden%20ceilings%2C%20Douglas%20fir%20pillars%2C%20and%20a%20range%20of%20art%20pieces%20%E2%80%94%20from%20a%20steel%20mural%20map%20of%20the%20surrounding%20landscape%20to%20large%20cowboy%20sculptures%20and%20paintings%20of%20local%20wildlife.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESince%20I%20visited%20during%20shoulder%20season%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20by%20the%20crowds%20in%20the%20downtown%20area.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20walk%20through%20an%20arch%20made%20of%20antlers%20into%20a%20park%20square%20with%20trees%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6723891d9b3250dbbceb5fdf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20town%20square%20in%20Jackson.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%2015%20minutes%20south%20of%20the%20airport%20is%20Downtown%20Jackson%2C%20the%20most%20developed%20area%20in%20Jackson%20Hole.%20I%20spotted%20a%20range%20of%20touristy%20shops%2C%20high-end%20boutiques%2C%20home%20decor%20stores%2C%20and%20plenty%20of%20restaurants%20and%20bars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20area%20seems%20to%20cater%20to%20tourists%20with%20fun%20photo%20ops%2C%20like%20antler%20arches%20in%20the%20town%20square.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20safe%20to%20say%20millions%20of%20tourists%20visit%20Jackson%20Hole%20each%20year.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nps.gov%2Fgrte%2Flearn%2Fnews%2F325-5-million-visits-to-national-parks-in-2023-3-4-million-visits-at-grand-teton.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Parks%20Service%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Grand%20Teton%20and%20Yellowstone%20National%20Park%20had%20roughly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nps.gov%2Fyell%2Flearn%2Fnews%2F24004.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E7.9%20million%20visitors%3C%2Fa%3E%20combined%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJackson%20Hole%20is%20a%20popular%20place%20for%20national%20park%20visitors%20to%20crash%2C%20especially%20in%20winter%20and%20summer.%20That's%20exactly%20why%20I%20visited%20in%20the%20fall%2C%20the%20destination's%20shoulder%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20wasn't%20nearly%20as%20crowded%20as%20Times%20Square%20in%20the%20wintertime%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20find%20streets%20busy%20with%20traffic%20and%20pedestrians%20in%20Jackson%20Hole%20%E2%80%94%20and%20most%20of%20the%20people%20on%20the%20street%20seemed%20to%20be%20tourists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20I%20lingered%20near%20this%20arch%20for%20almost%20an%20hour%20to%20get%20an%20unobstructed%20photo%2C%20but%20tourists%20stood%20in%20front%20of%20it%20for%20their%20own%20photos%2C%20one%20after%20another.%20I%20ended%20up%20settling%20for%20some%20crowded%20shots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20worth%20noting%20that%20I%20didn't%20even%20go%20to%20the%20national%20parks%2C%20where%20I%20imagine%20many%20of%20the%20town's%20overnight%20guests%20spend%20their%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELocal%20real-estate%20agent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fharlandbrothersrealestate.com%2Fagent%2Fsam-haack%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESam%20Haack%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20more%20travelers%20have%20been%20visiting%20during%20the%20offseason%20lately%2C%20leading%20to%20more%20traffic-filled%20months%20for%20locals%20in%20Jackson%20Hole.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20offseasons%20used%20to%20be%20much%20longer%2C%26quot%3B%20Haack%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20now%20that%20pricing%20for%20summer%20and%20winter%20hotel%20stays%20and%20restaurants%20has%20gone%20up%20so%20much%2C%20tourists%20are%20spilling%20over%20into%20the%20spring%20and%20fall%20for%20more%20affordable%20visits%2C%20cutting%20into%20locals'%20recovery%20time%20from%20the%20peak%20seasons.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20didn't%20expect%20the%20least%20expensive%20homes%20on%20the%20market%20to%20be%20conveniently%20located%20downtown.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20street%20with%20a%20red%20house%20on%20the%20left%2C%20a%20modern%20building%20on%20the%20right%2C%20and%20a%20tree-topped%20mountain%20in%20the%20background%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671fdbf19b3250dbbcea95c6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20home%20in%20downtown%20Jackson.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENYC's%20most%20expensive%20neighborhoods%20are%20generally%20the%20most%20conveniently%20located%20to%20the%20hustle%20and%20bustle%20(which%20is%20why%20I%20live%20in%20Queens).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20that%20wasn't%20the%20case%20in%20Jackson%20Hole.%20Most%20homes%20listed%20on%20Zillow%20for%20less%20than%20%241%20million%20are%20in%20the%20downtown%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Haack%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20wealthiest%20residents%20often%20reside%20in%20more%20remote%20areas%2C%20where%20homes%20can%20cost%20%2440%20million%20or%20more%2C%20like%20Teton%20Village%20and%20Wilson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20two%20areas%20are%20popular%20due%20to%20their%20more%20quiet%20nature%20as%20well%20as%20being%20outside%20the%20now%20traffic-filled%20town%20of%20Jackson%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJust%2015%20minutes%20from%20downtown%2C%20I%20felt%20worlds%20away%20from%20civilization.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20wide%20view%20of%20a%20valley%20between%20two%20hills%20and%20a%20large%20mountains%20in%20the%20background%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67056b4b3f2165d716df4cf5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Teton%20mountain%20range%20seen%20from%20the%20author's%20hotel%20balcony.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20home%20borough%2C%20Queens%2C%20the%20closest%20thing%20to%20a%20natural%20escape%20is%20Flushing%20Meadows%2C%20an%20898-acre%20space%20with%20open%20fields%2C%20trails%2C%20and%20mini%20forests.%20In%20the%20middle%2C%20it%20can%20almost%20feel%20like%20you're%20outside%20the%20city%20%E2%80%94%20as%20long%20as%20you%20close%20your%20ears.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20Jackson%20Hole%2C%20a%20short%20drive%20from%20downtown%20can%20make%20you%20feel%20like%20you're%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20nowhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20day%20one%20of%20my%20trip%2C%20I%20took%20a%2015-minute%20cab%20from%20the%20downtown%20area%20to%20my%20first%20accommodation%20just%20north%20of%20it%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhotel-yellowstone-jackson-hole-wyoming-adults-only-review-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadults-only%20Hotel%20Yellowstone%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20luxury%20resort%20sits%20on%20a%20hill%20with%20wide%20views%20of%20the%20Tetons%20and%20Snake%20River%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20soon%20as%20I%20stepped%20out%20of%20the%20car%2C%20I%20felt%20at%20peace.%20It%20was%20silent%2C%20save%20for%20the%20wind%20through%20the%20trees%20and%20the%20chirping%20birds.%20I%20thought%20I'd%20hear%20a%20highway%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20but%20no%2C%20this%20place%20was%20serene.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20night%20on%20my%20balcony%2C%20I%20watched%20the%20sunset%20over%20the%20Tetons%20and%20didn't%20listen%20to%20music%20as%20I%20normally%20would.%20Instead%2C%20I%20appreciated%20the%20sounds%20of%20nature%20and%20nothing%20else%20%E2%80%94%20a%20luxury%20I%20can't%20replicate%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20my%20first%20night%2C%20I%20was%20shocked%20to%20see%20a%20moose%20out%20the%20window%20while%20eating%20breakfast.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20images%3A%20Left%3A%20A%20moose%20walking%20on%20a%20hillside%20with%20a%20valley%20and%20mountains%20in%20the%20background.%20Right%3A%20Hotel%20units%20in%20wooden%20buildings%20with%20black%20rooftops%20behind%20a%20pond%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f45a260d59cc64f5b0313a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20moose%20at%20the%20author's%20hotel%20in%20Jackson%20Hole.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20surprising%20part%20of%20my%20trip%20popped%20up%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20day%20two.%20I%20sat%20at%20a%20small%20table%20next%20to%20the%20floor-to-ceiling%20windows%20at%20Hotel%20Yellowstone's%20restaurant%2C%20Olivia's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmid%20sipping%20my%20coffee%20and%20scarfing%20down%20steel-cut%20oats%2C%20I%20froze%20%E2%80%94%20a%20moose%20was%20walking%20along%20the%20property%2C%20and%20he%20couldn't%20have%20been%20more%20than%2010%20feet%20from%20my%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20New%20Yorker%2C%20my%20typical%20wildlife%20sightings%20consist%20of%20rats%2C%20squirrels%2C%20and%20raccoons.%20So%2C%20I%20stared%20at%20the%20creature%20in%20awe.%20It%20was%20like%20being%20at%20a%20zoo%20without%20the%20guilt%20of%20seeing%20caged%20animals%20as%20entertainment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20moose%20surprised%20me%2C%20but%20not%20my%20server%2C%20who%20said%20the%20animal%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bregular%26quot%3B%20and%20often%20swims%20in%20the%20pond%20and%20rolls%20in%20flower%20beds%20in%20the%20center%20of%20the%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20amazed%20that%20this%20majestic%2C%20wild%20creature%20could%20be%20so%20comfortable%20in%20a%20human%20space.%20But%20perhaps%20it's%20because%20I%20was%20at%20a%20calm%20establishment%20far%20from%20urban%20chaos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EUnlike%20New%20York%2C%20luxury%20homes%20in%20Jackson%20Hole%20are%20short%20and%20wide.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222801%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20exterior%20of%20a%20large%2C%20long%20house%20made%20of%20wood%20and%20concrete%20with%20an%20outdoor%20patio%20and%20nine%20lawn%20chairs%20in%20a%20green%20field%20with%20trees%20on%20the%20left%20and%20right%20with%20mountains%20in%20the%20background%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6723b707a0a0cc14f2254956%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222101%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20vacation%20home%20in%20Jackson%20Hole.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-worlds-highest-homes-billionaires-row-nyc-photos-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20wealthiest%20New%20Yorkers%20tower%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20100%20stories%20above%20the%20streets%20in%20glass%20skyscrapers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Jackson%20Hole's%20millionaires%20spread%20out%20ranch-style%20on%20several%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20as%20most%20buildings%20can't%20exceed%20three%20stories%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jacksonwy.gov%2F184%2FContractor-Licensing%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETown%20of%20Jackson%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20%3Cspan%3Espent%20two%20hours%20in%20one%20of%20these%20mansions%2C%20a%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-luxury-jackson