0to%20whom%20and%20why%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20everything%20is%20superlative%20and%20exaggerated%2C%20including%20a%20show%20of%20emotions%2C%20what%20happens%20to%20the%20normal-sized%20sentiments%3F%20When%20everything%20is%20already%20campy%2C%20how%20do%20you%20express%20the%20loss%20of%20something%20that%20was%20really%20grand%20to%20begin%20with%3F%20Like%20Rohit%20Bal's%20creative%20convictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20pioneers%20of%20the%20Indian%20fashion%20industry%20as%20we%20know%20it%20today%2C%20Rohit%20Bal%2C%20is%20dead%20at%2063%2C%20leaving%20behind%20a%20legacy%20of%20design%20sensibility%20that%20almost%20everyone%20admired%20and%20a%20persona%20that%20raised%20many%20an%20eyebrow.%20He%20seemed%20to%20care%20for%20neither%20and%20carried%20on%20regardless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBold%2C%20Just%20Like%20That%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBal's%20privileged%20family%20background%20allowed%20him%20to%20wade%20through%20the%20waters%20of%20uncertainty%20in%20a%20newly%20emerging%20industry%20in%20pre-liberalisation%20India.%20He%20launched%20his%20label%20in%201986%20when%20fashion%20was%20still%20not%20seen%20as%20a%20viable%20business%20in%20the%20country%20and%20luxury%20was%20seen%20only%20through%20the%20prisms%20of%20the%20Western%20outlook%20of%20consumerism%20and%20the%20exclusive%20extravagance%20of%20royalty.%20One%20of%20the%20first%20graduates%20of%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Fashion%20Technology%2C%20Bal%20was%20able%20to%20blend%20creativity%20and%20business%20to%20lead%20the%20way%20for%20at%20least%20three%20generations%20of%20Indian%20fashion%20designers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20set%20Bal%20apart%20from%20most%20of%20his%20peers%20and%20successors%20was%20his%20nonchalance%20about%20the%20risks%20he%20was%20taking.%20He%20was%2C%20for%20example%2C%20the%20first%20Indian%20fashion%20designer%20to%20start%20his%20restaurant.%20Veda%20was%20opened%20in%202005%20in%20Delhi's%20Connaught%20Place.%20To%20understand%20the%20audacity%20of%20this%20venture%2C%20consider%20this%3A%20Beige%20Alain%20Ducasse%20by%20Chanel%20opened%20in%20Tokyo%20in%202004%2C%20his%20contemporaries%20Dolce%20and%20Gabbana%20launched%20their%20Martini%20Bar%20in%20Milan%20in%202003%2C%20and%20Ralph%20Lauren's%20restaurant%20opened%20its%20doors%20in%20Chicago%20in%201999.%20Bal's%20design%20icon%2C%20Giorgio%20Armani%2C%20was%20the%20trendsetter%20in%20this%20fashion-culinary%20crossover%20when%20he%20launched%20his%20first%20restaurant%20in%20Paris%20in%201998.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECouture%20Meets%20Affordability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBal%20was%20also%20the%20first%20Indian%20fashion%20stalwart%20to%20start%20an%20exclusive%20line%20of%20childrenwear%2C%20%E2%80%98Bal%20Bachche'%2C%20in%202021.%20He%20betted%20on%20the%20emergent%20guilt-ridden%20parenting%20style%20of%20urban%20India.%20If%20you%20cannot%20give%20your%20children%20time%2C%20give%20them%20beautiful%20clothes%20at%20least.%20Bal's%20business%20decisions%2C%20including%20collaborations%20where%20he%20lent%20his%20name%20to%20products%2C%20were%20an%20extension%20of%20his%20personality%3A%20do%20what%20you%20feel%20is%20the%20correct%20thing.%20Not%20everything%20he%20did%20worked%20out%20as%20expected%2C%20but%20that%20didn't%20deter%20him%20from%20either%20exploring%20new%20business%20ways%20to%20expand%20his%20brand%20of%20fashion%20or%20tirelessly%20working%20on%20what%20made%20his%20brand%20unique.%20He%20wasn't%20threatened%20by%20the%20dilution%20that%20pret%20brings%20to%20any%20couturier's%20oeuvre.%20The%20grandiosity%20of%20couture%20easily%20dovetailed%20into%20Bal's%20more%20affordable%20clothes%20without%20reducing%20them%20to%20a%20pastiche.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDebroy's%20last%20published%20essay%20examined%20whether%20obituaries%20mean%20anything%20at%20all.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20lives%20my%20life%20has%20touched%2C%20improved%2C%20even%20bruised.%20If%20they%20get%20to%20know%2C%20they%20may%20remember%2C%20with%20fondness%20and%20bitterness.%20Such%20people%20don't%20write%20obituaries.%E2%80%9D%20In%20Bal's%20case%2C%20the%20obituaries%20and%20tributes%20are%20pouring%20in%20from%20people%20who%20are%20out%20there%20on%20society%20pages.%20Who's%20to%20tell%20whether%20the%20grief%20is%20real%2C%20manufactured%2C%20or%20imagined%3F%20In%20all%20the%20accounts%2C%20though%2C%20what%20shines%20through%20is%20Bal's%20irrepressible%20personality.%20A%20man%20who%20gave%20his%20all%20to%20things%2C%20ideas%2C%20and%20people%20that%20mattered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFashion%20Over%20Business%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20growing%20up%20during%20the%20turn%20of%20the%20millennium%2C%20Bal%20was%20iconic.%20Even%20those%20who%20did%20not%20know%20about%20his%20lotuses%20and%20peacocks%20knew%2C%20or%20at%20least%20speculated%2C%20about%20his%20love%20life.%20As%20if%20it%20was%20any%20of%20anyone's%20business.%20What%20he%20was%20doing%20back%20then%20for%20the%20indigenous%20handicraft%20traditions%20of%20Kashmir%20by%20catapulting%20them%20into%20a%20viable%20business%20scene%20through%20global%20visibility%20should%20have%20become%20everyone's%20business.%20Bal%20started%20the%20trend%20of%20diaphanous%20anarkalis%2C%20jalabiyas%2C%20and%20lehengas%2C%20which%20required%20a%20lot%20of%20fabric.%20The%20weavers%20benefitted%20from%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBal%20was%20often%20frustrated%20by%20how%20the%20Indian%20fashion%20scene%20was%20marred%20by%20cult%20worship%20and%20herd%20mentality.%20He%20was%20one%20of%20those%20few%20in%20the%20fashion%20business%20who%20actually%20cared%20more%20for%20fashion%20and%20less%20for%20business.%20He%20was%20aware%20that%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20his%20%E2%80%9Cfans%E2%80%9D%20were%20more%20interested%20in%20his%20personal%20life%20than%20in%20his%20designs.%20He%20was%2C%20however%2C%20conscious%20of%20the%20doors%20that%20his%20celebrity%20opened%20and%20acknowledged%20the%20same%20in%20many%20of%20the%20few%20interviews%20he%20gave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBal's%20growing%20cynicism%20around%20the%20fashion%20world%20went%20hand%20in%20hand%20with%20his%20growing%20commitment%20to%20creativity.%20Despite%20his%20health%20issues%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20do%20more%20and%20more%E2%80%94like%20adding%20layers%20to%20his%20unisex%20skirts.%20Only%20those%20in%20his%20innermost%20circle%20may%20be%20able%20to%20shed%20light%20on%20this%20contradiction.%20And%20that%20can%20happen%20only%20when%20the%20grandiosity%20of%20grief%20subsides.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Nishtha%20Gautam%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20author%20and%20academic.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730541360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fme6iukjo_rohit-bal_625x300_02_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frohit-bal-and-the-grandiosity-of-grief-6927795%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Designer%20Rohit%20Bal's%20growing%20cynicism%20around%20the%20fashion%20world%20went%20hand%20in%20hand%20with%20his%20growing%20commitment%20to%20creativity.%20Despite%20his%20health%20issues%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20do%20more%20and%20more%20-%20like%20adding%20layers%20to%20his%20unisex%20skirts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22WATCH%3A%20Akash%20Deep%20rattles%20Latham%E2%80%99s%20stumps%20with%20a%20fiery%20in-swinger%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730541213000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114880418%2Cimgsize-86658.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnew-zealand-in-india%2Fwatch-akash-deep-rattles-tom-lathams-stumps-with-a-fi