in)%20for%20Halloween%20in%20blue%20Philadelphia.%20Or%20that%20there's%20less%20support%20for%20Harris%20among%20some%20demographics%20in%20swing%20states%20compared%20to%20when%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-biden-maga-supporters-puerto-rico-election-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJoe%20Biden%3C%2Fa%3E%20won%20in%202020.%20New%20Hampshire%20and%20Virginia%20are%20turning%20red.%20Even%20X%20owner%20and%20Trump%20megadonor%20Elon%20Musk%20is%20extrapolating%20and%20framing%20early%20voting%20data%20to%20prematurely%20declare%20the%20prized%20swing%20state%20of%20Pennsylvania%20%26quot%3Bwill%20be%20a%20decisive%20Republican%20victory.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20election%20cycle%20where%20national%20and%20swing-state%20polls%20have%20been%20neck%20and%20neck%20for%20weeks%2C%20voters%20are%20taking%20to%20X%20and%20TikTok%20to%20confidently%20declare%20their%20candidate%20will%20win%20decisively.%20It's%20a%20response%20to%20a%20time%20of%20extreme%20anxiety%20and%20uncertainty%2C%20when%20Americans%20are%20more%20polarized%20than%20ever%20and%20have%20been%20told%20%26quot%3Bthis%20will%20be%20the%20last%20election%26quot%3B%20if%20their%20candidate%20does%20not%20win.%20There%20are%20maps%20covered%20in%20blue%20and%20opposing%20ones%20covered%20in%20red%2C%20with%20Electoral%20College%20predictions%20swaying%20wildly.%20%26quot%3BHarris%20is%20about%20to%20win%20in%20a%20blowout%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20says.%20Others%2C%20Musk%20included%2C%20point%20to%20an%20electoral%20map%20based%20on%20Polymarket%20election-betting%20odds%2C%20rather%20than%20polls%2C%20as%20evidence%20that%20Trump%20will%20win.%20Each%20individual%20post%20might%20not%20be%20so%20significant%20%E2%80%94%20if%20it%20weren't%20for%20powerful%20algorithms%20on%20TikTok%20and%20X%20that%20relentlessly%20push%20such%20posts%20out%20to%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20type%20of%20content%20that%20social%20sites'%20algorithms%20have%20long%20loved.%20Social-media%20conversations%20gather%20around%20extremes.%20People%20at%20the%20farthest%20ends%20of%20the%20ideological%20spectrum%20are%20most%20likely%20to%20post%20their%20views%20on%20social%20media%2C%20a%202021%20study%20from%20the%20Pew%20Research%20Center%20found.%20Social%20platforms'%20algorithms%20reward%20%26quot%3Bthis%20strong%20confidence%20and%20extreme%20opinions%20and%20engenders%20extreme%20reactions%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Ioana%20Literat%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20at%20Columbia%20University's%20Teachers%20College%20and%20the%20coauthor%20of%20%26quot%3BNot%20Your%20Parents'%20Politics%3A%20Understanding%20Young%20People's%20Political%20Expression%20on%20Social%20Media.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIf%20there's%20a%20video%20that%20says%2C%20'Polls%20are%20too%20close%20to%20tell%2C'%20that's%20not%20going%20to%20be%20the%20post%20that%20gets%20the%20most%20likes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20algorithms%20are%20in%20part%20to%20blame%2C%20we%20also%20have%20a%20deeply%20human%20aversion%20to%20uncertainty.%20To%20quiet%20the%20noise%2C%20we%20surround%20ourselves%20with%20others%20who%20feel%20confident%20that%20our%20shared%20candidate%20will%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20social%20platforms%20have%20sought%20to%20disentangle%20themselves%20from%20this%20kind%20of%20divisive%20political%20speech.%20In%202016%2C%20much%20brazen%20political%20dialogue%20took%20place%20on%20Facebook%2C%20where%20your%20opinionated%20uncle%20posted%20misinformation%20with%20abandon.%20For%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20Meta%20has%20pushed%20news%20out%20of%20Facebook%20feeds.%20And%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20company%20made%20further%20moves%20to%20de-emphasize%20political%20content%20on%20Instagram%2C%20Facebook%2C%20and%20Threads.%20All%20of%20this%20follows%20accusations%20that%20Facebook%20basically%20%26quot%3Bdestroyed%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20Megan%20Smith%2C%20the%20former%20chief%20technology%20officer%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20put%20it.%20Despite%20the%20efforts%20to%20change%2C%20deceptive%20political%20ads%20are%20still%20widespread%20on%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.propublica.org%2Farticle%2Ffacebook-instagram-meta-deceptive-political-ads-election%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EProPublica%20reported%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20week.%20Meta's%20%26quot%3Benforcement%20systems%20had%20already%20detected%20and%20disabled%20a%20large%20portion%20of%20the%20Pages%20%E2%80%94%20and%20we%20reviewed%20and%20took%20action%20against%20the%20remainder%20of%20these%20Pages%20for%20various%20policy%20violations%2C%26quot%3B%20Tracy%20Clayton%2C%20a%20Meta%20spokesperson%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20ProPublica.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%202016%20and%202020%20elections%2C%20the%20political%20reach%20of%20both%20X%20and%20TikTok%20have%20grown.%20A%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Ftechnology%2F2024%2F10%2F29%2Felon-musk-x-republican-democrat-twitter-election%2F%3Fpwapi_token%3DeyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.._swxWtRAVNu7JUVWoRNfQo9uNEN8IbkWnVcw-C_22eg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EWashington%20Post%20analysis%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20X%20published%20this%20week%20found%20that%20Republican%20leaders%20are%20gaining%20followers%20and%20going%20viral%20more%20often%20since%20Musk%20took%20over%20the%20platform.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fpolitics%2Felections%2Fx-twitter-political-content-election-2024-28f2dadd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EWall%20Street%20Journal%20analysis%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20newly%20created%20X%20accounts%20were%20often%20fed%20political%20content%2C%20even%20if%20they%20signed%20up%20looking%20for%20other%20topics%2C%20and%20that%20content%20leaned%20more%20heavily%20toward%20pro-Trump%20sentiments.%20(X%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20to%20comment%20on%20this%20story.)%20Meanwhile%2C%20half%20of%20the%2018-%20to%2029-year-olds%20surveyed%20by%20the%20Pew%20Research%20Center%20saying%20they%20watch%20political%20content%20on%20TikTok.%20A%20TikTok%20spokesperson%20declined%20to%20comment%20for%20this%20story%20but%20directed%20me%20to%20a%20webpage%20that%20says%20TikTok's%20policy%20is%20to%20label%20%26quot%3Bunverified%20election%20claims%2C%20make%20them%20ineligible%20for%20recommendation%2C%20and%20prompt%20people%20to%20reconsider%20before%20sharing%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20overconfident%20rhetoric%20isn't%20just%20polarizing%3B%20it%20could%20have%20more%20dangerous%20implications.%20%26quot%3BIf%20one%20side%20is%20expecting%20the%20race%20to%20be%20a%20blowout%20and%20the%20other%20side%20wins%2C%20that%20sort%20of%20lays%20the%20groundwork%20for%20broad%20support%20for%20challenging%20the%20results%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Sol%20Messing%2C%20a%20research%20associate%20professor%20at%20New%20York%20University's%20Center%20for%20Social%20Media%20and%20Politics.%20(Messing%20previously%20worked%20for%20Twitter%20but%20says%20he%20volunteered%20to%20be%20laid%20off%20when%20Musk%20bought%20the%20platform%20in%202022%2C%20and%20he%20refused%20severance%20to%20avoid%20signing%20a%20non-disparagement%20agreement.)%20%26quot%3BParts%20of%20this%20may%20reflect%20this%20broader%2C%20far-right%20strategy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20X%2C%20there%20is%20now%20an%20Election%20Integrity%20Community%2C%20launched%20by%20Musk's%20America%20PAC%20in%20late%20October.%20Here%2C%20people%20are%20encouraged%20to%20%26quot%3Bshare%20potential%20incidents%20of%20voter%20fraud%20or%20irregularities%20you%20see%20while%20voting%20in%20the%202024%20election%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20sightings%20they%20would%20typically%20report%20to%20official%20government%20agencies%20for%20investigation.%20Many%20of%20the%20recent%20posts%20show%20clear%20support%20for%20Trump%20in%20their%20claims%20of%20voting%20fraud%20and%20interference%3A%20On%20Thursday%2C%20one%20user%20posted%20photos%20of%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%20Ohio%20voting%20ballots%20with%20Trump's%20name%20misprinted.%20Election%20officials%2C%20however%2C%20say%20they%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cincinnati.com%2Fstory%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Felections%2F2024%2F10%2F31%2Fohio-election-officials-say-altered-trump-name-on-ballot-likely-a-hoax%2F75969483007%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Enot%20seen%20such%20ballots%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Trump%20has%20repeatedly%20said%20that%20the%20only%20way%20he'd%20lose%20is%20through%20election%20fraud%2C%20many%20posts%20from%20candidates%20and%20their%20famous%20endorsers%20don't%20express%20the%20same%20swaggering%20confidence%20we%20see%20across%20feeds.%20Ads%20for%20Harris%20on%20Instagram%20implore%20people%20to%20get%20to%20the%20polls%20and%20donate%20more%20money%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Ban%20all-hands-on-deck%20moment.%26quot%3B%20Michelle%20Obama%20says%20the%20race%20%26quot%3Bis%20too%20close%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bwe%20have%20to%20give%20it%20everything%20we've%20got.%26quot%3B%20And%20even%20Trump%20is%20back%20to%20posting%20on%20X%2C%20urging%20people%20to%20vote%20early%20%E2%80%94%20a%20shift%20from%202020%2C%20when%20he%20demonized%20mail-in%20voting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20on%20social%20media%20has%20the%20answer%20to%20what%20will%20happen%20in%20Tuesday's%20election.%20Anxiously%20reposting%20or%20liking%20election%20content%20may%20feel%20like%20the%20only%20thing%20we%20can%20do%20as%20the%20clock%20ticks%20down.%20%26quot%3BWe%20know%20it's%20a%20period%20of%20really%20high%20anxiety%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Literat.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20definitely%20shaped%20by%20the%20context.%20But%20it's%20also%20that%20content%20that%20really%20offers%20certainty%20or%20that%20resonates%20with%20hope%20or%20with%20fears%20that's%20spread%20more%20rapidly%2C%20too.%26quot%3B%20For%20now%2C%20the%20best%20way%20to%20alleviate%20that%20anxiety%20might%20be%20to%20get%20off%20social%20media%20until%20Tuesday%20passes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Famanda-hoover%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EAmanda%20Hoover%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%20covering%20the%20tech%20industry.%20She%20writes%20about%20the%20biggest%20tech%20companies%20and%20trends.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftwitter-trump-harris-landslide-election-anxiety-defense-mechanism-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730540761000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F672529a801ea6d83dee5b73a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftwitter-trump-harris-landslide-election-anxiety-defense-mechanism-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Social%20media%20users%20are%20deploying%20a%20classic%20defense%20mechanism%20for%20their%20election%20anxiety.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ahoover%40insider.com%20(Amanda%20Hoover)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftwitter-trump-harris-landslide-election-anxiety-defense-mechanism-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20running%20my%20first%20marathon.%20A%20sports%20dietitian%20helped%20me%20put%20together%20the%20perfect%20meal%20plan.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20collage%20of%20Julia%20Pugachevsky%20with%20healthy%20food%20items%20before%20a%20marathon%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6724e32301ea6d83dee59a26%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20you're%20prepping%20for%20a%20marathon%2C%20you%20want%20to%20swap%20side-salads%20for%20simple%20carbs.%3Cp%3EBURCU%20ATALAY%20TANKUT%2FGetty%2C%20lacaosa%2FGetty%2C%20Tyler%20Le%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECarbo-loading%20involves%20eating%20more%20carbohydrates%20to%20fuel%20up%20before%20a%20marathon.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EConsuming%20simple%20carbs%2C%20lean%20protein%2C%20and%20water%20helps%20you%20store%20energy%20before%20the%20race.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20also%20important%20to%20reduce%20fiber%20and%20fat%20intake%2C%20as%20well%20as%20avoid%20spicy%20or%20rich%20food.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20week%20before%20a%20marathon%2C%20runners%20are%20supposed%20to%20run%20fewer%20miles%20while%20carbo-loading%20%E2%80%94%20eating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-eat-carbs-without-blood-sugar-spikes-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20lot%20of%20carbohydrates%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20store%20up%20energy%20for%20the%20big%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20something%20I've%20been%20looking%20forward%20to%20as%20I%20prepare%20to%20run%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-avoid-hitting-wall-first-marathon-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20marathon%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20November%203.%20Oh%2C%20I%20%3Cem%3Ehave%20to%3C%2Fem%3E%20lie%20on%20the%20couch%20balancing%20a%20full%20pizza%20box%20on%20my%20stomach%3F%20I'm%20%3Cem%3Edoing%20the%20work%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20tenderly%20undressing%20a%20burrito%20in%20bed%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20the%20week%20is%20here%2C%20I%20want%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20make%20sure%20I%20eat%20right%20and%20don't%20just%20use%20carbo-loading%20as%20a%20hall%20pass%20to%20have%20cake%20every%20day.%20So%20I%20consulted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvictorem.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJena%20Brown%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20sports%20dietitian%20specializing%20in%20endurance%20racing%2C%20who%20reviewed%20my%20plan%20for%20the%20week%20and%20suggested%20improvements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20me%20I%20should%20aim%20for%20roughly%208-12%20grams%20of%20carbs%20a%20day%20per%20kilogram%20of%20my%20body%20weight.%20Not%20eating%20enough%20carbs%20before%20the%20race%20can%20impact%20my%20physical%20and%20mental%20performance%20%E2%80%94%20she%20said%20I%20will%20get%20tired%20sooner%2C%20have%20reduced%20endurance%2C%20and%20will%20feel%20like%20I'm%20working%20harder%20than%20I%20actually%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20did%20a%20calculation%2C%20and%20I%20should%20be%20aiming%20for%20508%20grams%20of%20carbs%20every%20day%2C%20broken%20down%20as%20169%20grams%20for%20three%20meals%20and%2085%20grams%20for%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20kinds%20of%20carbs%20I%20eat%20%E2%80%94%20as%20well%20as%20the%20foods%20I%20pair%20them%20with%20%E2%80%94%20are%20also%20crucial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22872635e7-cd89-4b36-9dd1-f2a2959e0cba%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFocus%20on%20lean%20protein%20with%20more%20carbs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20plate%20of%20salmon%20and%20spaghetti%20with%20tomatoes%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6723db0801ea6d83dee5816b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhile%20I%20usually%20prefer%20whole-wheat%20pasta%20because%20it%20has%20more%20fiber%20and%20minerals%2C%20I%20learned%20later%20that%20I%20should%20use%20regular%20pasta%20for%20easier%20digestion%20as%20I%20approach%20race%20day.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Pugachevsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20said%20eating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feasy-calculate-how-much-protein-coach-olympians-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotein%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20ideally%20from%20whole%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fultra-processed-foods-linked-early-death-study-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunprocessed%20foods%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20also%20highly%20important%20for%20athletic%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20go-to%20breakfast%20is%20peanut%20butter%20oatmeal.%20I%20use%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.urmc.rochester.edu%2Fencyclopedia%2Fcontent.aspx%3Fcontenttypeid%3D76%26contentid%3D20038-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20cup%20of%20oatmeal%3C%2Fa%3E%20(103g%20carbs%20and%2026g%20protein)%2C%20a%20scoop%20of%20peanut%20butter%20(8g%20protein)%2C%20and%20some%20berries%20(10g%20carbs).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20said%20this%20was%20a%20great%20choice%20because%20the%20oats%20provide%20protein%20in%20addition%20to%20carbs%2C%20while%20the%20berries%20add%20a%20few%20more%20carbs%20and%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fhealthy-fruits-and-vegetables%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eextra%20nutritional%20value%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20meal-prep%2C%20I%20made%20salmon%20and%20pasta%20in%20a%20butter-tomato%20sauce%20%E2%80%94%20a%20variation%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcooking.nytimes.com%2Frecipes%2F1024063-salmon-with-garlic-butter-and-tomato-pasta%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Times%20recipe%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20with%20roughly%2054g%20protein%20and%2064g%20carbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spoke%20to%20Brown%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20and%20she%20had%20one%20note%20for%20this%20dish%3A%20I%20stuck%20to%20whole-wheat%20pasta%20(my%20usual%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpasta-healthier-carbs-dietitian-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ego-to%3C%2Fa%3E)%20when%20regular%20pasta%20made%20with%20refined%20flour%20would%20be%20better%20for%20my%20pre-marathon%20digestion.%20(Regular%20pasta%20has%20just%20as%20much%20protein%20and%20carbs%20as%20whole%20wheat).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20explained%20that%20because%20of%20the%20volume%20of%20carbs%20I'll%20need%20to%20eat%2C%20consuming%20those%20higher%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgi-doctor-shares-3-tips-to-eat-more-fiber-without-bloating-or-gas-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiber%3C%2Fa%3E%20(like%20Ezekiel%20bread%2C%20my%20other%20favorite)%20will%20result%20in%20bloating%20and%20discomfort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20because%20I%20made%20this%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20week%2C%20I%20was%20still%20in%20the%20clear%3A%20Brown%20said%20the%20last%20three%20days%20of%20carbo-loading%20matter%20the%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b8d86e99-e827-4728-9fe5-2d1c3430a44c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20should%20consume%20more%20than%20half%20my%20body%20weight%20in%20fluids%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20holding%20a%20small%20donut%20and%20a%20smoothie.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6723dbae9b3250dbbceb8b9b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20smoothie%20and%20apple%20cider%20donut%3A%20it's%20called%20BALANCE.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Pugachevsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDrinking%20enough%20water%20is%20always%20important%2C%20but%20Brown%20said%20to%20ramp%20up%20my%20intake%20even%20more%20this%20week.%20%26quot%3BYou%20need%20extra%20fluid%20to%20store%20those%20carbohydrates%20in%20your%20muscles%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fam-i-drinking-too-much-water-2018-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyou%20don't%20want%20to%20overdo%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20dilute%20your%20sodium%20or%20electrolyte%20levels%20%E2%80%94%20both%20are%20very%20important%20for%20your%20running%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20normally%2C%20your%20bare%20minimum%20of%20fluids%20%E2%80%94%20including%20things%20like%20coffee%2C%20juice%2C%20or%20milk%20%E2%80%94%20should%20be%20half%20your%20body%20weight%20in%20ounces.%20This%20week%2C%20you%20should%20add%2020%20or%2030%20more%20ounces%20of%20water%20per%20day%2C%20so%20I%20should%20be%20aiming%20for%2090-100%20ounces%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhealthy-smoothie-recipes-athletes-longevity-biohacker-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmoothies%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20%26quot%3Bfantastic%26quot%3B%20because%20they're%20hydrating%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fwhat-are-electrolytes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealso%20include%20electrolytes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20After%20my%20shorter%20runs%20this%20week%2C%20I%20got%20a%20berry%20smoothie%20with%2055g%20carbs%20and%2027g%20protein%20(from%20protein%20powder).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20of%20the%20time%2C%20I've%20been%20setting%20reminders%20to%20drink%20more%20water%20and%20trying%20to%20get%20as%20much%20of%20it%20as%20I%20can%2C%20such%20as%20ordering%20a%20jumbo-sized%20seltzer%20at%20the%20movies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2275ee27f0-1ecd-40cd-9116-4987e24bbb60%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECut%20down%20on%20fiber%2C%20fat%2C%20and%20spice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222716%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20plate%20of%20pesto%20farfalle%20pasta%20with%20tomatoes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6723dbf5a0a0cc14f2255dd6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222037%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20used%20regular%2C%20refined%20flour%20pasta%20and%20blended%20pesto%20with%20cottage%20cheese%20to%20make%20the%20sauce.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Pugachevsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20three%20days%2C%20Brown%20said%20it's%20good%20to%20not%20go%20above%20the%20minimum%20recommended%20fiber%20and%20fat%20recommendations%20(no%20more%20than%2025g%20fiber%20for%20women%20and%2038g%20fiber%20for%20men%2C%20and%20not%20going%20over%200.45g%20fat%20per%20pound%20of%20bodyweight%2C%2063g%20for%20me).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPasta%20is%20great%2C%20but%20pasta%20covered%20in%20cheese%20or%20served%20with%20a%20side%20of%20broccoli%20can%20contribute%20to%20digestion%20problems%20and%20sluggishness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20one%20of%20the%20best%20runs%20I%20ever%20had%20was%20the%20day%20after%20I%20ate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-tried-high-protein-cottage-cheese-recipe-tiktok-pasta-eggs-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecottage%20cheese%20pasta%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20low%20in%20fat%20and%20high%20in%20protein%20and%20carbs%20%E2%80%94%20a%20half-cup%20of%20cottage%20cheese%20is%2014g%20of%20protein%2C%20while%20a%20package%20of%20cooked%20pasta%20is%20about%20111g%20of%20carbs.%20I've%20meal-prepped%20it%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20came%20the%20question%20I%20was%20most%20curious%20about%3A%20what's%20the%20best%20thing%20to%20eat%20the%20night%20before%3F%20I%20ask%20because%20I%20often%20get%20%26quot%3Brunner's%20trots%26quot%3B%20on%20long%20runs%20and%20want%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarathon-runner-pooped-pants-rescued-kitten-race-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eavoid%20the%20fate%20of%20so%20many%20past%20marathon%20runners%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I'm%20hoping%20to%20give%20my%20sensitive%20stomach%20the%20best%20shot%20at%20not%20making%20me%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboston-marathon-runner-caught-pooping-on-strangers-lawn-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enational%20headline%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20said%20to%20avoid%20spicy%20food%20or%20anything%20too%20rich.%20The%20best%20meals%20would%20be%20pasta%20in%20a%20tomato%20sauce%20or%20a%20baked%20potato%2C%20light%20on%20toppings.%20On%20the%20morning%20of%20the%20marathon%2C%20I'll%20want%20to%20stick%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Fcomplex-carbs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esimple%20carbs%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20sugars%20that%20are%20easier%20to%20digest%20quickly%2C%20like%20a%20plain%20bagel%20and%20some%20Gatorade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarbo-loading%20didn't%20end%20up%20being%20as%20thrilling%20as%20I%20thought.%20I%20daydreamed%20about%20going%20all%20out%20at%20an%20Ethiopian%20restaurant%20or%20challenging%20how%20many%20rolls%20an%20all-you-can-eat%20sushi%20place%20is%20willing%20to%20serve%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20said%20the%20temptation%20to%20have%20a%20fancy%2C%20celebratory%20dinner%20before%20the%20race%20is%20normal.%20But%20she%20recommended%20either%20making%20food%20at%20home%20or%20looking%20at%20the%20menu%20ahead%20of%20time%20(rather%20than%20excitedly%20making%20a%20game-time%20decision).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20friend%20booked%20us%20a%20table%20at%20a%20ramen%20spot%20for%20the%20night%20before.%20I%20will%20follow%20Brown's%20advice%20and%20order%20a%20lighter%20vegan%20broth%20with%20noodles%20and%20seaweed%20instead%20of%20the%20cheese-and-chili-oil%20pizza-fusion%20option%20my%20heart%20longs%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20bright%20side%2C%20she%20said%20decadent%20meals%20are%20totally%20fine%20%3Cem%3Eafter%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20marathon.%20That's%20all%20the%20motivation%20I%20need%20to%20cross%20that%20finish%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-eat-before-running-marathon-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730540701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6724e3929b3250dbbceba33c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-eat-before-running-marathon-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20sports%20dietitian%20helped%20me%20curate%20the%20perfect%20diet%20before%20running%20a%20marathon.%20The%20trick%20is%20to%20eat%20simple%20carbs%20and%20less%20fiber%2C%20and%20avoid%20salads.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpugachevsky%40businessinsider.com%20(Julia%20Pugachevsky)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-eat-before-running-marathon-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cheesemakers%20left%20reeling%20after%20a%20'bizarre'%20heist%20of%20cheddar%20worth%20almost%20%24400%2C000%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Artisanal%20cheesemaker%20Tom%20Calver%20of%20Westcombe%20Dairy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6724f3b601ea6d83dee5a2c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETom%20Calver's%20company%20was%20one%20supplier%20hit%20by%20the%20cheese%20heist.%3Cp%3EMatt%20Austin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAlmost%2050%2C000%20pounds%20of%20artisanal%20cheese%20were%20stolen%20in%20a%20sophisticated%20heist%20in%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20fraudster%20posed%20as%20a%20French%20distributor%20and%20took%20delivery%20of%20the%20large%20order.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20small%20companies%20involved%20now%20face%20losses%20and%20uncertainty%20despite%20police%20making%20an%20arrest.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20sophisticated%20cheese%20heists%20in%20history%20has%20left%20British%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffrench-cheesemakers-struggle-to-meet-standards-due-to-climate-change-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echeesemakers%3C%2Fa%3E%20reeling%20and%20facing%20an%20uncertain%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2021%2C%20fraudsters%20posing%20as%20a%20French%20wholesaler%20stole%2022%20metric%20tons%20(about%2048%2C500%20pounds)%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-traditional-english-cheddar-cheese-made-aged-caves-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBritish%20cheddar%20cheese%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Neal's%20Yard%20Dairy%2C%20a%20specialist%20cheese%20wholesaler%20and%20retailer%20based%20in%20London%2C%20outlets%20including%20BBC%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeal's%20Yard%20unwittingly%20delivered%20the%20cheese%2C%20estimated%20to%20be%20worth%20about%20%C2%A3300%2C000%20(%24390%2C000)%2C%20to%20the%20fraudsters%20before%20realizing%20they%20were%20not%20legitimate%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Metropolitan%20Police%20told%20Business%20Insider%20a%2063-year-old%20man%20has%20since%20been%20arrested%20on%20suspicion%20of%20fraud%20by%20false%20representation%20and%20handling%20stolen%20goods%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20case%20and%20released%20on%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cheesemaker%20Tom%20Calver%20surveys%20wheels%20of%20cheese%20at%20Westcombe%20Dairy%20in%20the%20UK.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6724f40ca0a0cc14f2257f3a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22914%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECheesemakers%20say%20the%20fraudsters%20executed%20a%20sophisticated%20scam.%3Cp%3EMatt%20Austin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cheese%20is%20still%20missing%2C%20but%20those%20keenest%20to%20solve%20the%20mystery%20are%20the%20cheesemakers%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20so%20bizarre%20because%20how%20do%20you%20get%20rid%20of%20that%20much%20cheese%20and%20get%20a%20decent%20return%20on%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20Ben%20Ticehurst%2C%20dairy%20manager%20and%20head%20cheesemaker%20at%20Trethowan%20Brothers%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20believes%20the%20scam%20was%20meticulously%20planned%2C%20as%20his%20company%20was%20initially%20contacted%20about%20the%20fraudulent%20order%20in%20June.%20He%20also%20said%20the%20fraudsters%20%26quot%3Basked%20all%20the%20right%20questions%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20the%20age%20profile%20of%20the%20cheese%2C%20which%20didn't%20raise%20any%20red%20flags.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20came%20across%20as%20totally%20genuine%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20things%20that%20made%20it%20so%20appealing%20was%20thinking%20that%20we'd%20see%20British%20cheese%20in%20a%20French%20supermarket.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20quantity%20requested%20and%20the%20involvement%20of%20an%20international%20client%2C%20Trethowan%20Brothers%2C%20which%20supplied%20about%20half%20the%20order%2C%20worked%20with%20two%20other%20suppliers%20as%20well%20as%20Neal's%20Yard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20rallied%20around%20to%20try%20and%20fulfill%20the%20order%20because%20it%20was%20obviously%20going%20to%20be%20relatively%20good%20for%20us%20and%20also%20for%20Neal's%20Yard%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tom%20Calver%2C%20director%20of%20Westcombe%20Dairy%2C%20another%20supplier%20caught%20up%20in%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20incredibly%20sophisticated%20and%20also%20really%20quite%20surprising%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BOut%20of%20all%20the%20things%20that%20one%20could%20steal%2C%2022%20tonnes%20of%20artisanal%20cloth-bound%20cheddar%20probably%20wouldn't%20be%20high%20up%20on%20very%20many%20people's%20list%2C%20I%20would%20assume%2C%20but%20here%20we%20are.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220291a644-8c0f-4f7c-9cd3-66c87005b970%5C%22%3EHanging%20in%20the%20balance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20suppliers%20are%20still%20shocked%20by%20the%20theft%2C%20they've%20escaped%20any%20loss%20as%20Neal's%20Yard%20has%20borne%20the%20full%20financial%20brunt%20of%20the%20heist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20a%20purely%20balance%20sheet%20point%20of%20view%2C%20we've%20actually%20had%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20orders%20we%20ever%20had%2C%26quot%3B%20Ticehurst%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Brothers%20Todd%20and%20Maugan%20Trethowan%20run%20an%20artisanal%20cheese%20business%20together.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6724f5b301ea6d83dee5a361%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrothers%20Todd%20and%20Maugan%20Trethowan%20run%20an%20artisanal%20cheese%20business.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Trethowan%20Brothers%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Lockwood%2C%20director%20of%20Neal's%20Yard%20Dairy%2C%20told%20BI%20the%20theft%20will%20affect%20their%20annual%20results%20and%20cashflow%2C%20but%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bcore%20of%20the%20business%20is%20strong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20few%20years%20we%20hope%20to%20look%20back%20at%20a%20bad%20year%20that%20made%20us%20stronger%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20suppliers%20hope%20the%20media%20coverage%20of%20the%20incident%20raises%20the%20profile%20of%20British%20cheddar%2C%20they're%20wary%20of%20the%20longer-term%20impact%20it%20will%20have%20on%20a%20key%20wholesaler%20and%20champion%20of%20British%20artisanal%20cheese%20makers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a5066b55-f1c7-472d-b0e4-c20338ec87e0%5C%22%3E'Honesty%20and%20trust'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20Neal's%20Yard%20who%20took%20that%20real%20hit%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they've%20always%20been%20such%20a%20force%20for%20good%20in%20the%20world%20of%20cheese%2C%26quot%3B%20Ticehurst%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20industry%20is%20based%20on%20a%20lot%20of%20honesty%20and%20trust%2C%20so%20it's%20difficult%2C%26quot%3B%20Calver%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarting%20an%20artisan%20cheddar%20business%20is%20an%20expensive%20and%20laborious%20endeavor%2C%20Ticehurst%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEquipment%20can%20cost%20about%20%C2%A3750%2C000%20(%24974%2C000)%20and%20artisanal%20cheese%20can%20take%20at%20least%2012%20months%20to%20mature%2C%20meaning%20it%20can%20take%20more%20than%20a%20year%20to%20see%20any%20return%20on%20investment%2C%20Ticehurst%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20his%20boss%2C%20Todd%20Tretho