ere%20concentrated%20in%20areas%20where%20Russia%20was%20on%20the%20attack%2C%20this%20meant%20lighter%20coverage%20of%20Kursk.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20in%20late%201944%20%E2%80%94%20even%20as%20Germany%20was%20reeling%20from%20massive%20defeats%20in%20Normandy%20and%20by%20an%20advancing%20Russia%20on%20the%20Eastern%20Front%E2%80%94%20Hitler%20and%20his%20top%20advisers%20identified%20the%20Ardennes%20region%20of%20Belgium%20as%20a%20weak%20spot%20in%20the%20center%20of%20the%20Allied%20lines.%20While%20American%20and%20British%20forces%20were%20concentrated%20to%20the%20north%20and%20south%20for%20a%20final%20offensive%20into%20Germany%2C%20the%20Allies%20considered%20the%20hilly%2C%20wooded%20terrain%20of%20the%20Ardennes%20a%20quiet%20sector%20safe%20to%20defend%20with%20a%20few%20depleted%20or%20inexperienced%20divisions.%20The%20heavy%20forests%20could%20serve%20as%20cover%20for%20the%20German%20infantry%20and%20Panzer%20armored%20forces%20as%20they%20advanced.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20its%20August%20assault%2C%20the%20Ukrainian%20high%20command%20also%20took%20care%20to%20keep%20words%20of%20the%20operation%20to%20as%20few%20people%20as%20possible.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20intelligence%20was%20collected%20and%20analyzed%2C%20the%20Commander-in-Chief%20of%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20General%20Oleksandr%20Syrskyi%2C%20led%20the%20planning%20with%20only%20a%20few%20senior%20officers%20in%20attendance%2C%26quot%3B%20TRADOC%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20planning%20sessions%20were%20likely%20conducted%20face-to-face%20to%20prevent%20the%20risk%20of%20Russian%20cyber%20actors%20or%20signals%20intelligence%20from%20discovering%20the%20plan.%20Press%20interviews%20with%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20indicate%20that%20the%20incursion%20forces%20were%20not%20notified%20until%20hours%20before%20the%20operation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20conceal%20its%20preparations%2C%20Ukraine%20also%20resorted%20to%20disinformation%2C%20such%20as%20spreading%20the%20word%20that%20the%20Ukrainian%20army%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-wont-be-able-launch-new-offensive-year-nato-official-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewouldn't%20be%20capable%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20launching%20an%20offensive%20before%20spring%202025.%20Ukrainian%20troops%20were%20unwitting%20parts%20of%20the%20deception.%20For%20example%2C%20%26quot%3BUkraine's%20military%20announced%20the%2061st%20Mechanized%20Brigade%20would%20be%20moving%20to%20Vovchansk%2C%20a%20city%20in%20the%20northern%20sector%20of%20the%20fighting%20in%20eastern%20Ukraine%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20TRADOC.%20%26quot%3BEven%20after%20the%2061st%20was%20told%20they%20would%20go%20into%20Russia%2C%20senior%20officers%20in%20the%20unit%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20bluff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELikewise%2C%20knowledge%20of%20the%20Ardennes%20offensive%20%E2%80%94%20codenamed%20Operation%20Wacht%20am%20Rhein%20%E2%80%94%20was%20confined%20to%20a%20small%20circle%20of%20officers%20sworn%20to%20secrecy%20upon%20pain%20of%20death.%20Allied%20cryptographers%20had%20broken%20high-level%20German%20radio%20codes%20(the%20%26quot%3BUltra%26quot%3B%20program)%2C%20but%20German%20forces%20employed%20radio%20silence%2C%20and%20orders%20were%20conveyed%20by%20courier%20and%20telephone.%20Even%20the%20name%20Wacht%20am%20Rhein%20(%26quot%3BWatch%20on%20the%20Rhine%26quot%3B)%20was%20meant%20to%20convince%20Allied%20intelligence%20that%20it%20was%20a%20defensive%20plan%20to%20stop%20an%20Allied%20crossing%20of%20the%20Rhine%20River%20into%20Germany.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUkraine%20prepped%20its%20offensive%20by%20blinding%20Russian%20ISR%20with%20strikes%20on%20Russian%20airfields%2C%20as%20well%20as%20using%20Ukrainian%20drones%20to%20destroy%20Russian%20UAVs.%20To%20delay%20a%20Russian%20response%2C%20Ukraine%20used%20rockets%2C%20drones%20and%20artillery-delivered%20mines%20against%20airbases%20and%20command%20and%20control%20centers%2C%20as%20well%20as%20interdicting%20Russian%20reinforcements.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20too%20echoed%20Nazi%20Germany's%20final%20offensive.%20It%20had%20timed%20the%20Ardennes%20operation%20to%20coincide%20with%20a%20long%20spell%20of%20bad%20weather%2C%20which%20grounded%20Allied%20reconnaissance%20planes.%20On%20the%20misty%20dawn%20of%20Dec.%2016%2C%201944%2C%20a%20massive%20German%20artillery%20barrage%20disrupted%20American%20communications%2C%20while%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nationalww2museum.org%2Fwar%2Farticles%2Foperation-greif-secret-mission-sow-chaos-us-army%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EGerman%20commandos%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%94%20dressed%20in%20American%20uniforms%20%E2%80%94%20infiltrated%20US%20lines%20to%20spread%20confusion%20and%20panic.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20question%20for%20Ukraine%20is%20whether%20its%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbattle-of-kursk-ukraine-russia-railroad-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EKursk%20operation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20will%20fare%20better%20than%20the%20Bulge.%20Instead%20of%20a%20breakthrough%20that%20changed%20the%20tide%20of%20World%20War%20II%2C%20the%20German%20offensive%20eventually%20bogged%20down%20because%20of%20poor%20terrain%2C%20lack%20of%20fuel%20and%20fierce%20American%20resistance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20seizing%20some%20Russian%20territory%20and%20creating%20dismay%20in%20Moscow%2C%20Ukraine's%20offensive%20has%20failed%20to%20divert%20Russian%20forces%20from%20eastern%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20Russian%20counterattacks%20are%20shrinking%20the%20Ukrainian%20salient.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENonetheless%2C%20Ukraine%20has%20shown%20that%20surprise%20attacks%20are%20possible%20even%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farmies-need-their-own-drone-air-force-flown-by-specialists-study-says-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDrone%20Age%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Ukrainian%20incursion%20into%20the%20Kursk%20region%20demonstrated%20that%20operational%20surprise%20is%20still%20possible%20in%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict%20by%20avoiding%20and%20degrading%20ISR%20%E2%80%94%20a%20lesson%20that%20could%20broadly%20be%20applied%20to%20future%20large-scale%20combat%20operations%20in%20other%20theaters%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20TRADOC%20concluded.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EMichael%20Peck%20is%20a%20defense%20writer%20whose%20work%20has%20appeared%20in%20Forbes%2C%20Defense%20News%2C%20Foreign%20Policy%20magazine%2C%20and%20other%20publications.%20He%20holds%20an%20MA%20in%20political%20science%20from%20Rutgers%20Univ.%20Follow%20him%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2F%40mipeck1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ETwitter%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fmipeck%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ELinkedIn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-russia-kursk-incursion-ww2-battle-of-the-bulge-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730539322000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6723ce7ba0a0cc14f225593d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-russia-kursk-incursion-ww2-battle-of-the-bulge-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ukraine's%20invasion%20of%20Russia's%20Kursk%20region%20used%