C%20the%20country's%20KCNA%20state%20news%20agency%20reported%20on%20Friday.%20It%20said%20it%20achieved%20a%20maximum%20altitude%20of%20close%20to%207%2C700%20km%20(around%204%2C780%20miles).%20Japan's%20defense%20ministry%20has%20supported%20these%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKCNA%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnorth-korea-military-officials-helping-russia-ukraine-win-for-kim-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENorth%20Korean%20leader%20Kim%20Jong%20Un%3C%2Fa%3E%20oversaw%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20missile%2C%20which%20it%20identified%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BHwasongpho-19.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVideo%20footage%20from%20North%20Korean%20state%20media%20reshared%20by%20NK%20News%20on%20X%20appears%20to%20show%20the%20missile's%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EVIDEO%3A%20North%20Korean%20state%20media%20published%20footage%20of%20the%20launch%20of%20a%20new%20intercontinental%20ballistic%20missile%20(ICBM)%20model%20called%20the%20%E2%80%9CHwasong-19%E2%80%9D%20on%20Thursday.%20Read%20more%20here%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FkA8m36NARX%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FkA8m36NARX%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FCXXlBJX7O5%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FCXXlBJX7O5%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20NK%20NEWS%20(%40nknewsorg)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnknewsorg%2Fstatus%2F1852167422456807495%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%201%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20most%20striking%20feature%20of%20the%20new%20missile%20is%20its%20size.%20It%20has%20been%20estimated%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fnorth-korea-missile-launch-united-states-4173ce128b8336b2cb315a3bf62c6980%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eat%20least%2092%20feet%20long%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20more%20than%2030%20feet%20longer%20than%20the%20US's%20LGM-30G%20Minuteman%20III%20ICBM.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhotos%20released%20by%20KCNA%20show%20the%20missile%20being%20carried%20by%20a%20huge%20transporter%20erector%20launcher%20(TEL).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221996%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kim%20Jong%20Un%20next%20to%20the%20Hwasongpho-19%20TEL.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67255f7901ea6d83dee5c2a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221310%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKim%20Jong%20Un%20next%20to%20the%20Hwasongpho-19%20TEL.%3Cp%3EKCNA%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EVirginie%20Grzelczyk%2C%20a%20specialist%20on%20North%20Korea%20and%20the%20Dean%20of%20the%20School%20of%20Social%20Sciences%20and%20Humanities%20at%20Aston%20University%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20solid-fuel%20missiles%20like%20the%20Hwasongpho-19%20offer%20a%20%26quot%3Bpotentially%20greater%20payload%20capacity%2C%20including%20the%20possibility%20of%20carrying%20nuclear%20warheads.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20the%20Hwasong-19%2C%20being%20notably%20large%2C%20may%20face%20operational%20challenges%20regarding%20mobility%20in%20a%20conflict%2C%26quot%3B%20Grzelczyk%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEdward%20Howell%2C%20a%20Korea%20Foundation%20fellow%20at%20Chatham%20House's%20Asia-Pacific%20Program%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20%26quot%3Bas%20missiles%20get%20bigger%20and%20bigger%2C%20questions%20of%20effectiveness%20will%20always%20be%20raised.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Hwasong-19%20missile%20may%20be%20able%20to%20support%20a%20heavy%20warhead%2C%20but%20as%20the%20size%20of%20a%20missile%20increases%2C%20its%20mobility%20decreases%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20this%20latest%20test%2C%20North%20Korea%20had%20la