20his%202015%20show%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20Qutub%20Minar%2C%20or%20a%20gender-bender%20show%20featuring%20male%20models%20in%20ghagra%20skirts%20and%20sindoor.%20And%20then%20there%20was%20his%20historic%20Lodhi%20show%2C%20where%20models%20wore%20richly-embroidered%20outfits%20and%20walked%20into%20a%20pool%2C%20resembling%20lilies%20and%20lotuses.%20(Fun%20fact%3A%20He%2C%20too%2C%20later%20jumped%20into%20the%20pool!)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20Bal%20drew%20inspiration%20from%20his%20Kashmiri%20heritage%2C%20with%20floral%20and%20peacock%20motifs%20becoming%20synonymous%20with%20his%20label%20launched%20in%201989.%20The%20embroidery%20was%20rich%20and%20his%20deep%20understanding%20of%20Indian%20textiles%20was%20evident.%20His%20expertise%20lay%20in%20marrying%20luxurious%20fabrics%2C%20bold%20colours%2C%20detailing%20and%20silhouettes%20to%20put%20on%20display%20the%20cultural%20heritage%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20no%20wonder%20then%20that%20his%20label%20expanded%20quickly%20to%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20Europe%20and%20his%20designs%20adorned%20a%20plethora%20of%20Indian%20and%20international%20personalities%2C%20including%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%2C%20Aishwarya%20Rai%20Bachchan%2C%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20Khan%2C%20Sonam%20Kapoor%2C%20Uma%20Thurman%2C%20Cindy%20Crawford%2C%20Naomi%20Campbell%20and%20Pamela%20Anderson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20website%2C%20Bal%20described%20himself%20as%20a%20designer%20who%20%26quot%3Bcombines%20the%20right%20mix%20of%20history%2C%20folklore%2C%20village%20craft%2C%20and%20dying%20arts%20to%20create%20imaginative%20and%20innovative%20masterpieces%20for%20catwalks%20and%20fashion%20talks%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELong%20before%20the%20age%20of%20mass%20apparel%20production%20leading%20to%20movements%20advocating%20equitable%20earnings%20of%20artisans%2C%20Rohit%20Bal's%20emphasis%20on%20the%20craftsman's%20contribution%20was%20evident%20in%20his%20work.%20He%20also%20played%20mentor%20to%20many%20designers%20in%20he%201990s%2C%20including%20Pankaj%20and%20Nidhi%20and%20Sahil%20Kochhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20dipped%20his%20toes%20in%20the%20world%20of%20food%2C%20opening%20the%20rustic%20Veda%20and%20laidback%20Cibo%20in%20Delhi.%20Rohit%20Bal%20also%20found%20his%20way%20to%20the%20silver%20screen%2C%20appearing%20in%20Hollywood%20film%20True%20West%20and%20Indian%20films%20Monsoon%20Wedding%20and%20Boom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20Bal%20called%20his%20last%20show%20'Kaynaat'%20a%20celebration%20of%20%26quot%3Bthe%20bloom%20of%20life%20and%20beauty%26quot%3B.%20Like%20all%20his%20work%20in%20a%20career%20spanning%20over%20three%20decades%2C%20the%20collection%20is%20a%20reminder%20that%20classic%20elegance%20outlives%20time%2C%20generations%20and%20an%20ever-changing%20fashion%20aesthetic.%20As%20the%20curtains%20come%20down%20on%20the%20designer's%20illustrious%20life%2C%20his%20creations%20will%20go%20from%20being%20tools%20of%20beauty%20and%20expression%20to%20stories%20and%20art.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730537340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fme6iukjo_rohit-bal_625x300_02_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frohit-bal-master-of-fabric-and-fantasy-leaves-a-legacy-of-elegance-6927433%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rohit%20Bal%2C%20lovingly%20called%20'Gudda'%20but%20also%20termed%20'Enfant%20terrible'%2C%20is%20synonymous%20with%20fashion%20shows%20that%20broke%20norms%2C%20remained%20timeless.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frohit-bal-master-of-fabric-and-fantasy-leaves-a-legacy-of-elegance-6927433%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2216-year-old%20girl%20jumps%20into%20well%20after%20boyfriend%20commits%20suicide%20in%20UP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730537033000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.co