5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20in%20San%20Jose%2C%20California%2C%20Luke%20Durant's%20historic%20finding%20has%20been%20classified%20as%20a%20Mersenne%20prime%2C%20named%20after%20French%20monk%20Marin%20Mersenne.%20He%20studied%20these%20numbers%20over%20350%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20report%2C%20Mersenne%20primes%20are%20rare%2C%20making%20Durant's%20discovery%20even%20more%20impressive.%20In%20simple%20terms%2C%20to%20consider%20a%20number%20as%20Mersenne%20prime%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20written%20in%20the%20form%20'2%E1%B5%96-1'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20other%20large%20prime%20numbers%20are%20used%20in%20some%20applications%20for%20protecting%20internet%20security%2C%20the%20Mersenne%20primes%20remain%20crucial%20for%20other%20key%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20historical%20record%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20prime%20tells%20us%20something%20about%20the%20historical%20capability%20of%20computers%2C%20and%20in%20particular%20it%20tells%20us%20something%20about%20the%20progress%20of%20humanity%20in%20this%20area%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2Fscience%2Fworld-largest-prime-number-found%2Findex.html%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%20quoted%20Dr%20Kevin%20Buzzard%2C%20professor%20of%20pure%20mathematics%20at%20Imperial%20College%2C%20London%2C%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Durant's%20research%20was%20announced%20on%20October%2021%20by%20the%20Great%20Internet%20Mersenne%20Prime%20Search%20(GIMPS)%2C%20a%20community-based%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20example%20of%20citizen%20science%2C%20GIMPS%20allows%20non-specialists%20to%20discover%20the%20largest%20known%20primes%2C%20according%20to%20Buzzard%20%26quot%3BI%20recognised%20that%20the%20GIMPS%20community%20has%20put%20together%20an%20incredible%20system%20with%20amazing%20technology%20for%20searching%20for%20huge%20prime%20numbers%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Durant%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20project%2C%20Luke%20Durant%20first%20got%20himself%20familiar%20with%20its%20software%20and%20learned%20to%20use%20cloud%20computers.%20Later%20on%2C%20he%20combined%20these%20elements%20that%20enabled%20him%20to%20run%20enough%20worldwide%20systems%20for%20creating%20an%20incredibly%20speedy%20supercomputer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20from%20different%20cities%20around%20the%20world%20are%20volunteers%20in%20the%20GIMPS%20community%20as%20they%20run%20the%20project's%20software%20on%20their%20personal%20computer%20systems%20to%20search%20for%20new%20primes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELuke%20Durant%20was%20inspired%20to%20hunt%20for%20the%20world's%20largest%20primes%20due%20to%20his%20interest%20in%20developing%20large%20computing%20systems%20as%20well%20as%20exploring%20the%20limitations%20of%20the%20laws%20of%20physics.%20Through%20his%20effort%2C%20he%20%26quot%3Bwanted%20to%20push%20the%20boundaries%20of%20the%20known%20universe%20in%20whatever%20small%20way%20I%20was%20able%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20enormous%20prime%20numbers%20are%2C%20in%20some%20senses%2C%20the%20largest%20'unique%20pieces%20of%20information'%20in%20the%20known%20universe%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730527680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fqto0dmv_prime-number_625x300_02_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fformer-nvidia-programmer-discovers-prime-number-containing-more-than-41-million-digits-6926165%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2036-year-old%20man%2C%20who%20earlier%20worked%20as%20a%20programmer%20for%20Nvidia%2C%20spent%20around%20a%20year%20of%20his%20life%20and%20invested%20a%20considerable%20amount%20of%20money%20to%20discover%20the%20world's%20largest%20known%20prime%20number.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fformer-nvidia-programmer-discovers-prime-number-containing-more-tha