managed%20to%20bridge%20the%20past%20with%20the%20present%20and%20the%20traditional%20with%20the%20modern.%20Debroy%20belonged%20to%20this%20select%20club.%20One%20won't%20find%20many%20who%20can%20elaborate%20on%20the%20forces%20of%20%26quot%3Bcreative%20destruction%26quot%3B%20as%20described%20by%20Joseph%20Schumpeter%20and%20simultaneously%20decode%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20hidden%20messages%20in%20the%20Puranas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDebroy%20Sir%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20this%20author%20called%20him%2C%20passed%20away%20too%20soon%2C%20at%20the%20young%20age%20of%2069%3B%20he%20still%20had%20tons%20of%20wisdom%20to%20offer.%20But%20then%2C%20such%20is%20life.%20The%20co-author%20had%20last%20met%20Debroy%20Sir%20in%20his%20Niti%20Ayog%20office%20on%20September%2010.%20The%20meeting%20involved%20a%20personal%20exchange%20of%20ideas%20and%20also%20an%20update%20on%20the%20work%20that%20the%20CVoter%20Foundation%20had%20been%20doing%20for%20the%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20since%20October%202022.%20Sir%20looked%20visibly%20unwell.%20After%20talking%20a%20bit%20about%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20results%20and%20some%20more%20about%20the%20next%20report%20CVoter%20Foundation%20would%20submit%2C%20the%20co-author%20left%20with%20a%20promise%20from%20Sir%20that%20they%20would%20meet%20again%20after%20Deepavali.%20On%20the%20way%20out%2C%20the%20co-author%20checked%20with%20Mr.%20Krishnan%2C%20his%20secretary%2C%20and%20asked%20about%20Sir's%20health.%20Krishnan%20had%20confirmed%20that%20he%20was%20very%20unwell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Debroy%20Fought%20Against%20Obsolete%20Laws%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20would%20write%20about%20Debroy's%20tremendous%20capacity%20to%20straddle%20the%20world%20of%20ancient%20wisdom%20alongside%20modern%20dilemmas%20that%20affect%20the%20ordinary%20citizen.%20He%20toiled%20through%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20pages%20of%20%26quot%3Blaws%26quot%3B%20dating%20back%20to%20the%2019th%20century%20when%20the%20British%20ruled%20India.%20Hundreds%20of%20obsolete%20laws%20have%20been%20eliminated%20since%20Narendra%20Modi%20became%20prime%20minister%20in%202014.%20Some%20credit%20for%20that%20is%20definitely%20due%20to%20Debroy%2C%20who%20unflinchingly%20researched%2C%20wrote%20and%20talked%20about%20the%20damage%20such%20silly%20laws%20were%20doing%20to%20India.%20Even%20till%20recently%2C%20Debroy%20was%20persistent%20with%20his%20efforts%20in%20identifying%20and%20red-flagging%20needless%20regulations%2C%20rules%20and%20red%20tape.%20And%20while%20doing%20this%2C%20he%20managed%20to%20find%20time%20to%20translate%20dozens%20of%20ancient%20texts%20from%20Sanskrit%20into%20easy%20English%20that%20even%20young%20Indians%20could%20relate%20to.%20The%20output%20he%20produced%20was%20simply%20staggering.%20That%20was%20not%20all.%20The%20authors%20have%20seldom%20come%20across%20a%20more%20prolific%20columnist%20in%20contemporary%20India.%20The%20issues%20that%20he%20so%20deftly%20analysed%20without%20ideological%20posturing%20and%20verbose%20English%20should%20be%20a%20lesson%20for%20budding%20scholars%20and%20analysts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20the%20authors%20admired%20most%20about%20him%20was%20his%20integrity%20and%20spine.%20For%20many%20years%2C%20Debroy%20headed%20the%20research%20activities%20of%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20Foundation%2C%20which%20was%20headed%20by%20the%20then%20UPA%20chairperson%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20her%20close%20advisors.%20Sometime%20after%20the%20UPA%20came%20to%20power%20in%202004%2C%20the%20Foundation%20started%20rating%20and%20ranking%20states%20on%20their%20performance%20based%20on%20a%20series%20of%20governance%20parameters.%20The%20Foundation%20ranked%20Gujarat%2C%20then%20led%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20as%20the%20best-performing%20state.%20According%20to%20various%20media%20reports%2C%20the%20Congress%20top%20brass%20was%20very%20upset%20with%20this.%20The%20differences%20were%20too%20deep%2C%20and%20Debroy%20resigned.%20As%20a%20dignified%20person%2C%20he%20never%20publicly%20talked%20about%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20he%20had%20to%20leave%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20Foundation.%20He%20was%20also%20malevolently%20targeted%20on%20social%20media%20by%20a%20section%20of%20people.%20To%20his%20credit%2C%20Debroy%20simply%20preferred%20to%20ignore%20the%20abuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlunt%20And%20Open%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDebroy%20was%20doing%20all%20this%20even%20as%20he%20served%20as%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20(EAC)%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20Some%20think%20that%20the%20position%20is%20largely%20a%20ceremonial%20one.%20But%20he%20absolutely%20did%20not%20fall%20into%20the%20category%20of%20a%20happy%20and%20satisfied%20'courtier'.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20the%20authors%20personally%20presented%20some%20of%20the%20most%20unflattering%20data%20points%20to%20him.%20But%20to%20our%20surprise%2C%20he%20understood%2C%20and%20rather%20than%20softening%20the%20pinch%2C%20he%20always%20asked%20us%20to%20point%20things%20out%20even%20more%20bluntly%2C%20if%20possible.%20He%20believed%20our%20job%20was%20to%20dig%20out%20the%20bad%20news%20on%20economic%20matters%20upfront%20from%20the%20public%20perception%20data%20that%20we%20collect.%20Some%20of%20the%20sharpest%20minds%20in%20India%20have%20been%20members%20of%20the%20advisory%20board%20under%20him%2C%20and%20many%20institutions%2C%20big%20and%20small%2C%20have%20conducted%20research%20on%20its%20behalf%20on%20a%20range%20of%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20co-author%2C%20the%20passing%20away%20of%20Debroy%20Sir%20is%20also%20a%20personal%20loss.%20More%20than%2040%20years%20ago%2C%20he%20was%20a%20Master's%20student%20at%20the%20Gokhale%20Institute%20of%20Politics%20%26amp%3B%20Economics%20in%20Pune%2C%20where%20Debroy%20was%20a%20young%20professor.%20Since%20then%2C%20he%20has%20considered%20Debroy%20Sir%20to%20be%20a%20mentor.%20The%20lead%20author%20regrets%20not%20meeting%20him%20more%20often.%20He%20has%20seldom%20met%20a%20scholar%20with%20such%20an%20open%20mind%2C%20a%20blunt%20but%20fair%20attitude%2C%20and%20a%20unique%20sense%20of%20humour.%20For%20the%20lead%20author%2C%20what%20was%20most%20admirable%20about%20Debroy%20Sir%20was%20his%20devotion%20to%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20needs%20credible%20data.%20And%20it%20needed%20a%20polymath%20giant%20like%20Bibek%20Debroy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Yashwant%20Deshmukh%20is%20the%20Founder%20%26amp%3B%20Editor-in-Chief%20of%20CVoter%20Foundation%20and%20Sutanu%20Guru%20is%20Executive%20Director)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730527020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F2ha36tjk_bibek-debroy-ani_160x120_01_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbibek-debroy-the-man-devoted-to-data-6926436%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Over%20the%20years%2C%20the%20authors%20personally%20presented%20some%20of%20the%20most%20unflattering%20data%20points%20to%20Bibek%20Debroy.%20But%20to%20our%20surprise%2C%20he%20understood%2C%20and%20rather%20than%20softening%20the%20pinch%2C%20he%20always%20asked%20us%20to%20point%20things%20out%20even%20more%20bluntly%2C%20if%20possible%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbibek-debroy-the-man-devoted-to-data-6926436%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20SRK%20bashed%20celebs%20who%20left%20their%20partners%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730526530000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114872996%2Cimgsize-965486.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%