.com%2Fstory%2Fus-election-the-tiny-village-in-india-which-is-cheering-kamala-harris-on-as-she-aims-for-the-white-house-13245497%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESky%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20has%20brought%20such%20glory%20to%20this%20village.%20No%20one%20has%20ever%20done%20so%20much%20for%20us%20-%20even%20if%20they%20tried%20for%20decades%20and%20centuries.%20It's%20unimaginable!%20Our%20village%20is%20world%20famous%20because%20of%20her%2C%20and%20we%20repeatedly%20thank%20her%2C%20wish%20her%20all%20the%20best%20and%20our%20blessings%20are%20always%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20N%20Krishnamurthy%2C%20an%2080-year-old%20retired%20bank%20manager.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20villager%20told%20the%20outlet%20that%20Ms%20Harris%20has%20%26quot%3Bbrought%20fame%20to%20womanhood%20-%20all%20the%20women%20here%20are%20so%20proud%20of%20her%20achievements.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20inspired%20by%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Madhumita%2C%20a%2019-year-old%20student.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMani%2C%20who%20runs%20a%20grocery%20shop%20beside%20the%20temple%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20be%20so%20happy%20and%20proud%20when%20she%20wins%20and%20will%20celebrate%20with%20sweets.%20But%20we%20will%20be%20even%20happier%20if%20she%20remembers%20our%20village%20-%20that%20would%20be%20enough%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20village%20may%20be%20disappointed%20it%20didn't%20get%20a%20mention%20in%20any%20of%20the%20vice%20president's%20speeches%2C%20Ms%20Harris'%20grandfather%20is%20still%20remembered%20fondly%20as%20a%20well-read%20man%20with%20progressive%20values%20and%20a%20passion%20for%20activism%20that%20he%20passed%20down%20to%20his%20daughters%2C%20Shyamala%20and%20Sarala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fauthor-reveals-donald-trump-and-epsteins-controversial-bet-involving-princess-diana-6922481%5C%22%3EAuthor%20Reveals%20Don