%20in%20Iran.%20Retaliatory%20strikes%20between%20the%20three%20countries%20have%20caused%20widespread%20destruction%2C%20recently%20hitting%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu's%20residence%20in%20the%20coastal%20city%20of%20Caesarea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeveloped%20by%20Rafael%20Advanced%20Defense%20Systems%2C%20architect%20of%20Israel's%20Iron%20Dome%2C%20and%20Elbit%20Systems%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rafael.co.il%2Fsystem%2Firon-beam%2F%5C%22%3EIron%20Beam%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20engage%20at%20the%20speed%20of%20light%20from%20a%20range%20of%20hundreds%20of%20meters%20to%20several%20kilometers.%20It%20has%20an%20unlimited%20magazine%2C%20almost%20zero%20cost%20per%20interception%20and%20causes%20minimal%20collateral%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20defence%20ministry%20said%20that%20the%20Iron%20Beam%20will%20shoot%20down%20the%20smaller%20projectiles%2C%20while%20larger%20targets%20like%20ballistic%20missiles%20will%20be%20tackled%20by%20the%20Arrow%202%20and%20Arrow%203%20interceptors.%20The%20system%20will%20heat%20and%20destroy%20the%20target%2C%20including%20drones%2C%20which%20are%20small%2C%20light%20and%20have%20a%20low%20radar%20signature%2C%20making%20them%20tough%20targets%20for%20the%20Iron%20Dome%2C%20experts%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2024%2F11%2F01%2Fmiddleeast%2Fisrael-iron-beam-laser-system-intl%2Findex.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECNN%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20system%20will%20function%20at%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20cost%20that%20goes%20into%20operating%20the%20Iron%20Dome.%20Tel%20Aviv%20think%20tank%20Institute%20for%20National%20Security%20Studies%20said%20each%20interceptor%20missile%20fired%20by%20the%20Iron%20Dome%20costs%20approximately%20%2450%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20system%2C%20however%2C%20does%20not%20operate%20well%20in%20low%20visibility%20conditions%2C%20including%20inclement%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%