nt-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20school%20places%20an%20emphasis%20on%20extracurricular%20activities.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20this%2C%20the%20trust%20got%20on%20board%20Shyamala%20Manikandan%20as%20an%20honorary%20alumni%20director%2C%20to%20mentor%2C%20and%20in%20a%20way%2C%20become%20guardians%20for%20these%20children%20even%20after%20they%20graduated%20from%20the%20school.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20an%20after-school%20programme%20for%20our%20alumni.%20Part-time%20teachers%20conduct%20special%20classes%20for%20students%20from%20Classes%208%20to%2012%20over%20the%20weekend.%20We%20provide%20them%20with%20all%20the%20necessary%20tools%20they%20need%20to%20succeed.%20We%20have%20partnered%20with%20local%20high%20schools%20to%20ensure%20a%20smooth%20transition%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Srinivasan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foundation%20also%20covers%20students%E2%80%99%20college%20fees%2C%20provides%20laptops%20for%20their%20studies%2C%20and%20more.%20Thanks%20to%20these%20efforts%2C%20many%20students%20have%20completed%20their%20graduation.%20Some%20have%20become%20engineers%2C%20others%20are%20training%20to%20become%20chartered%20accountants%20or%20entering%20finance%2C%20one%20is%20pursuing%20an%20MBBS%2C%20and%20Pavan%20is%20even%20working%20toward%20a%20doctorate.%20Several%20have%20completed%20industrial%20training%20and%20now%20work%20with%20reputable%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20students%20reach%20Class%207%2C%20the%20alumni%20director%20discusses%20their%20preferred%20high%20schools%20and%20helps%20arrange%20admissions.%20By%20Class%2010%2C%20students%20receive%20career%20counselling%20and%20are%20asked%20to%20select%20their%20top%20three%20colleges%2C%20with%20TCF%20assisting%20in%20securing%20their%20placements.%20The%20foundation%20also%20offers%20personal%20coaching%20in%20subjects%20like%20maths%2C%20science%2C%20economics%2C%20statistics%2C%20business%20studies%2C%20computer%20skills%20and%20English%20to%20support%20students%20after%20school%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBreaking%20the%20cycle%3A%20Education%20as%20a%20pathway%20out%20of%20poverty%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20break%20the%20shackles%20of%20poverty.%20A%20house-help%E2%80%99s%20daughter%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20follow%20her%20mother%E2%80%99s%20profession.%20She%20should%20do%20what%20she%20wants%2C%20and%20the%20only%20way%20to%20do%20it%20is%20through%20education%2C%E2%80%9D%20emphasises%20Srinivasan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPavan%E2%80%99s%20mother%20works%20as%20a%20house-help%2C%20and%20his%20father%20is%20a%20driver.%20He%20is%20the%20first%20person%20in%20his%20family%20to%20even%20complete%20Class%2010.%20%E2%80%9CI%20honestly%20would%20have%20continued%20in%20this%20cycle%20of%20poverty%20if%20it%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20been%20for%20TCF.%20Without%20their%20guidance%2C%20I%20would%20have%20probably%20become%20a%20driver%20like%20my%20father%20after%20Class%2010.%20They%20helped%20me%20in%20every%20step%20of%20the%20way%2C%20right%20from%20choosing%20a%20college%20to%20paying%20the%20fees%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-18-at-12.49.37-1-1730296482.jpeg%3Ffit%3D1080%252C495%26quality%3D89%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pavan%20teaching%20students%20at%20the%20school%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-18-at-12.49.37-1-1730296482.jpeg%3Fw%3D1080%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-10-18-at-12.49.37-1-1730296482.jpeg%3Fresize%3D300%252C138%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%2030