%20of%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20months%20of%20research%2C%20she%20started%20a%20WhatsApp%20group%20in%202022.%20Through%20word%20of%20mouth%20and%20sharing%20it%20with%20patients%20and%20friends%2C%20the%20group%20quickly%20began%20to%20grow.%20Initially%2C%20Dr.%20Sumitra%20managed%20all%20the%20calls%20and%20messages%20herself%2C%20offering%20the%20service%20for%20free.%20Soon%2C%20parents%20began%20sharing%20it%20with%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20get%20calls%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country%2C%20including%20remote%20villages%20from%20Rajasthan%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20more.%20From%20250%20members%2C%20we%20grew%20to%20500%20over%20a%20few%20months.%20Soon%2C%20I%20was%20handling%20more%20than%201%2C000%20questions%20daily%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20Gurugram%20resident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20patient%20numbers%20increased%2C%20Dr%20Sumitra%20onboarded%20additional%20doctors%20to%20provide%20round-the-clock%20support.%20Babynama%20now%20has%2050%20paediatricians%20on%20board%20who%20offer%20chat%20support%20till%2011%20pm%20and%20call%20support%2024%2F7.%20She%20also%20started%20thinking%20of%20ways%20to%20reach%20more%20people%2C%20thus%20creating%20pages%20on%20Instagram%20and%20YouTube%20to%20educate%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20sustain%20the%20service%2C%20she%20eventually%20introduced%20a%20small%20consultation%20fee%20of%20Rs%20100%20per%20call.%20By%20March%202023%2C%20with%20over%201%2C000%20daily%20queries%20and%201%2C000%20members%2C%20Babynama%20expanded%20to%20a%20full-fledged%20website%20and%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20paediatric%20care%20accessible%3A%20How%20Babynama%2